Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.69,0:00:10.05,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,When watching Hayate no Gotoku, make sure to watch at a good distance away from the TV in a well lit room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:23.75,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,So good~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:28.11,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,It's already February...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.52,0:00:31.64,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,I've yet to see Hayate-kun once this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.24,0:00:34.71,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,But soon, the greatest opportunity of the year will come!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.71,0:00:38.08,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the biggest event for all girls in February is-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.52,0:00:42.44,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, mister. What do you think you're doing in front of a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.44,0:00:43.55,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:49.77,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Oni stay out! 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:53.53,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Setsubun: An activity to ward off Oni by throwing roasted beans on February 3rd.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:51.29,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Luck stays in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.29,0:00:53.53,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Oni stay out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:55.93,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Um, why are we doing this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.47,0:00:58.17,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:03.67,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,She's right. The biggest event in February has to be this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.41,0:01:10.25,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,That is all right, but Nagi, it's getting late, so please start getting ready for bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.18,0:01:15.68,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Then let's end this by eating your age's worth in beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.68,0:01:16.35,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.35,0:01:17.35,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.62,0:01:20.52,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,How about you, Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.13,0:01:24.13,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I guess I will, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.51,0:01:30.29,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, all of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.29,0:01:31.77,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,What were you staring at?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:32.94,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:34.14,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:44.87,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you were thinking that there's not enough beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:46.48,Default,2,0000,0000,0000,,No, absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.99,0:01:50.82,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who looks at you, you're a fresh seventeen year old.{seven year old or seventeen years old? - Al}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:55.38,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you drenched in sweat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:03.44,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, go to bed now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.44,0:02:05.00,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,An Oni was inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.24,0:02:11.64,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Did you all know that there's a huge mansion like this in the middle of Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.64,0:02:13.90,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The name of the mistress who lives there is Sanzenin Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:14.75,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.88,0:02:18.93,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Her butler's name is Ayasaki Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:20.86,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The two are slightly airheaded...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:23.13,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,...and they misunderstand each other a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.13,0:02:28.21,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,...but they are bound by a tight master-butler bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:30.43,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, why are they such...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.43,0:02:33.36,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Oh no, my lower back. It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:15.94,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh darn. We made Maria mad again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:17.39,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,You don't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:19.40,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give her too much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:22.10,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,She's not forever young.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:24.35,Default,2,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such a scary thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:27.63,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,But, Maria has been working without any breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:32.44,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,She may be the best of all professional maids, but she must be letting fatigue pile up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:37.42,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,We are always in her great care,\Nso it'd be nice if we could show our appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:41.62,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Then I shall become a maid and-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:44.83,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, Maria-san will become even more tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.31,0:04:48.01,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,But she's not the kind of person who will take a break even if you tell her to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:50.21,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,E-Exactly as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:54.12,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right. That's a perfect plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:55.27,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,A plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:59.38,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Approximately one hour later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:02.48,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:06.52,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going all of a sudden? {ep 44}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:08.72,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where. {ep 44}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:11.06,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a surprise for when we get there. {ep 44}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:23.64,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:26.38,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, we're staying here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:29.47,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, Saki-san gave us some input.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.73,0:05:34.01,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies Overnight Plan, Relaxation Tour?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:36.38,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,A friend of mine went there the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:40.71,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Stay at an expensive hotel in the middle of the city, enjoy the spa and aesthetic salon,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.86,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,forget about work, and relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:47.43,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it's popular among young working women as a gift to themselves for working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:48.61,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Young...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:49.99,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,...working women.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:53.51,Default,2,0000,0000,0000,,Young... Young... Young...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:54.30,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,That's the key word?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:55.90,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:57.96,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Get right to it, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:58.66,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:05.98,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, we call it, "Maria-san, thank you so much all the time. Gratitude to our Onee-sama, Relax Plan." {ep 44}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.98,0:06:07.58,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,What? But, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.35,0:06:12.82,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,This is a present from Milady as a sign of our gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.82,0:06:16.61,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Maria, thank you so much for working so hard for us all the time. {ep 44}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:20.90,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,But for today and tomorrow, forget about your work and enjoy a vacation in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.95,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:28.68,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll take your offer and have a good rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:31.38,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Relax all you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:32.68,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:33.39,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:36.31,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.57,0:06:44.60,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew that Hayata-kun and the others would come to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.03,0:06:51.09,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the room over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:53.72,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Maria and I will use that room then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:56.42,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,First, let me get some tea ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:07:00.52,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Maria-san, you're on vacation, so please don't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:02.78,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:05.57,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate prepared lots of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:08.50,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,The pool, jacuzzi, gym, aesthetic salon, and nail salon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.50,0:07:10.13,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You can use any facility as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:07.50,Default-alt,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? This is the imperial suite; I'd like to order room service.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:09.58,Default-alt,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,A pot of royal milk tea, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:14.99,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently this hotel's sales point is service towards young women.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:19.21,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect for a young working woman like Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:22.84,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to emphasize "young" so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:27.88,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. It's room service.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:30.33,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:36.39,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,So? Don't I look good in this? Did I surprise you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:38.08,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Class rep? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:41.18,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,It's a one day experience event at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.18,0:07:43.66,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen it on the news before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:45.31,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:48.13,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:52.15,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well for some reason, today's a 5%-off service day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:54.56,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,That's the reason I chose this place, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:55.77,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:08:00.48,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. Today, this hotel is covered by Hakuou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:02.80,Default,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,I saw Hayata-kun and his group here just a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:03.66,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:08.66,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping Oo**** or Yoshi**** were coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.66,0:08:11.45,Default,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshi****? Because we're right in front of the Tokyo Metropolitan Government Building?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.45,0:08:13.41,Default,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Oh whatever. Where's Hina, by the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:14.84,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,She got trapped with the manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:22.26,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Looking back at it now, it was back when\Nthe Tokyo Olympics were going on that I started this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:24.03,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get a sense of the timeframe at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.03,0:08:28.39,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, you've got to get this right!\NWe need to have Maria enjoy the vacation. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:30.68,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. My habit of saving on things took over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:30.39,Default-alt,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:33.59,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:35.25,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Maria-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:36.94,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,See what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:38.14,Default-alt,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it, Maria-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:42.98,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what did all of you come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:44.56,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:50.12,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,That's such a great story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:51.70,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm touched!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:53.44,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.44,0:08:54.51,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell everyone, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:55.46,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Segawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:57.22,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I have a...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:59.92,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,...really bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.92,0:09:04.99,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Um... If it's about me, please don't worry. I'm already relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.49,0:09:08.20,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,No! We can't give up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:10.33,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,We must protect Maria's break no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:12.31,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:14.92,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Milady and Maria-san, please proceed on to Plan 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:16.53,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,We'll meet back here in three hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:17.88,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:19.05,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:23.35,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why is this starting to feel like a battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:26.61,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,She's right. This is a form of battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:37.69,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,How is it, Maria? Relaxing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:39.62,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:43.16,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Oh wow! It's like a rose bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:45.20,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,But wait, this is the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:49.67,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Strange. I don't recall asking for service like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:51.27,Default,Him,0000,0000,0000,,No need for your thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:52.48,Default,Him,0000,0000,0000,,Take this instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:59.31,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:01.96,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Himuro, is this enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:04.85,Default,Him,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Was it educational, Sir Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:07.08,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Working sure is hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:09.92,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Hayate was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:14.36,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no... People from Hakuou are here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:16.33,Default,Non,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:21.66,Default,Non,0000,0000,0000,,At that rate, you can't possibly give the customers satisfactory service.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:20.30,Default-alt,Azu,0000,0000,0000,,Leg... my leg... This is impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:29.15,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Next we'll go for the aesthetic salon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:31.70,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you get relaxed this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:34.15,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes. But, Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.89,0:10:39.33,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Why the Super Special Marvelous Anti-Aging Course?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:41.09,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let the details bother you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:42.80,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be in the room next door!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.17,0:10:45.19,Default,Robo,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.80,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're the trash robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:49.75,Default,Robo,0000,0000,0000,,Please come right over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:52.93,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're surprisingly pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:56.73,Default,Rob,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, since I always give massages to Makimura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:08.31,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll go get relaxed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:09.65,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:13.59,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the story from Segawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.59,0:11:15.70,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why is even Katsura-sensei here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:22.09,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,It was an opportunity to try, and also,\NI wanted to learn some new skills in case I get fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:28.47,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Leave everything to me.\NI'll do everything to make you relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:32.71,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a serious error... I mean...\Na serious danger threatening me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:37.72,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh. This is so relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.43,0:11:43.79,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,This is so good~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:43.06,Default-alt,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like being a teacher really wears you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.82,0:11:51.08,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,And before I know it, I'm already twenty-eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:56.19,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Makes me wonder if I can continue to live the way I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:12:03.27,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,But, you are who you are, so no matter how much you worry, you can't become another individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:05.61,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,So please always be yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.61,0:12:08.24,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,But do watch out how much you drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:11.04,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,You feel this? It's the pressure point for your liver.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:14.75,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Maria-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:18.33,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,It... It feels like I just met a role model for life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:24.09,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm more than ten years younger than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:26.94,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Maria, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:29.23,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I just sensed a strange atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:31.16,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:38.27,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I just sensed a bad omen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.18,0:12:50.88,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Your new dress looks great on you, Kuzuha-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:52.88,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,It's specially made by COSPA.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:56.82,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,I must be dressed in formal attire like this all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:12:58.97,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You look so great, Kuzuha-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:02.74,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Shion. Before we start the tour, let's go raise our blood sugar level.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:03.83,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Kuzuha-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.46,Default,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:08.87,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It's heading away from relaxation and continues on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.46,0:13:13.87,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Nonbiri yuttari.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.46,0:13:13.87,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Nonbiri yuttari. = Relax and make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:16.97,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,Rizumu de shiritori suta-to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:16.97,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Rizumu de shiritori suta-to. = Starting rhythmical shiritori.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.97,0:13:18.81,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Tan tan tan nta. Matteru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.97,0:13:18.81,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Tan tan tan nta. Matteru. = Tan tan tan nta. Now waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:25.52,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they're both enjoying the city vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:30.38,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hayate! I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:33.05,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back. But where's Maria-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:36.80,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,She said she'll take a stroll in the garden to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:38.56,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,"Relax", she said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:41.13,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. "Relax" it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:51.00,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! Since Maria won't be coming back to the room for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:54.12,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate and I are alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:55.61,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make some tea right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:14:00.42,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, we're in a suite that newly-wed couples are likely to stay in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:04.41,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.41,0:14:05.66,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:14.54,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,It's not easy to take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:18.00,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,But, since the two of them are being considerate... 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:24.33,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,During the time I'm here, I must respond to their thoughts by having a slow day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:26.08,Default,Isu,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:28.33,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Isumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:34.21,Default,Isu,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Um... There's something I'd like to ask.\NMight this be where Hakuou's practical training event is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:36.09,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:40.00,Default,Isu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:44.26,Default,Isu,0000,0000,0000,,I was finally able to make it to a destination in episode 45.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:48.45,Default,Isu,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I would never make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:50.74,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway, let's go to the front desk together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:58.00,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a surprise that you're going to be part of an event like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:02.95,Default,Isu,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to learn about society through the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:04.64,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Maria-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:06.00,Default-alt,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Maria-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:06.55,Default-alt,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Maria-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.64,0:15:06.55,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the Hakuou students.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:12.09,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:14.68,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:17.56,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's too quiet in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:18.70,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Let's turn the TV on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:20.53,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:24.04,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no. This would get Hayate in the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:26.03,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,As much as we love each other, it's too early for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.03,0:15:27.37,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:30.54,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I like this actress quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:34.89,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since she broke up with the kabuki actor,\Nshe's been doing much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:40.72,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, what is Maria doing? How long does she have to relax until she's satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:43.12,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,She was not relaxing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:53.25,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,See? The trick is to tuck both bed sheets and the cover and line them up properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:54.63,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Maria-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:59.18,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,I just double booked a room by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:06.27,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. We're very sorry. We can get a room with\Ntwin beds ready instead of double beds, if that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:08.81,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Maria-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.81,0:16:16.03,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes. The year I came over here was the year of the Osaka Expo, 1971.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:18.12,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Oh please, Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:20.95,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,The Osaka Expo was in 1970.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:26.71,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly, the total number of guests was 64,218,770 people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:31.62,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,The number of countries participating, including Japan, was 77 countries and 4 international authorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:34.74,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me for a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:39.44,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, Maria-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:43.01,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,But, isn't today your day off? You don't need to go rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:46.22,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Please keep this a secret from Nagi and Hayate-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:49.35,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,We're in trouble, Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:52.66,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,Mari-pon. What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:53.61,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Mari-pon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:55.34,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Makimura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:58.75,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you two know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:00.43,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, through certain circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:04.62,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness. I want to ask you a favor regarding something, Maria-chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:05.81,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Maria-chi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:07.23,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:10.58,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the cafeteria is high schooling and is in trouble! {talking giberish}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:17.35,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Milady. Please stop staying on six.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:18.86,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.86,0:17:20.90,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Who else can it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.34,0:17:25.30,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:26.79,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Mari-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:29.84,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Keep it a secret that this call is from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.63,0:17:33.18,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.67,0:17:38.89,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Maria-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:41.61,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maria-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:46.02,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,I was cleaning up a room\Nand found a customer's forgotten item.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:47.54,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,What was the room number?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:49.05,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look up the contact information.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.68,0:17:51.88,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Um, where is the Concierge?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:53.98,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I sent him over that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.98,0:17:55.55,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Um, sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:57.86,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Nihao. Wo jiao Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:57.86,Note,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Note: This is Chinese for "Hello. My name is Maria."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:17:59.39,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Maria-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:03.17,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Please keep this a secret from Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.17,0:18:04.59,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:06.72,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,So, why did you call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:09.23,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask for a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:13.37,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the next treat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.37,0:18:14.80,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:21.93,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,We were making sweets at high speed to keep up with your orders, but the pâtissier collapsed from being overloaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:24.93,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,Weak! I've not yet had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:26.98,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:29.72,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,This is a hidden menu, special Mont Blanc.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:32.69,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.75,0:18:41.07,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,This is concentrated yet simple,\Nwhile the sweetness covers the tongue like velvet! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:42.40,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,It's that good?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:46.14,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,So good~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:48.52,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,I'm satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:52.70,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,I quit the tour. Before I snap out of this enchanted feeling, I'm heading back to the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.70,0:18:53.60,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:58.20,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Maria-san's recipe works great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:19:01.12,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,After all, its effect was proven in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.12,0:19:03.56,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:06.12,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, Makimura-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:10.98,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm just reading books and eating cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:13.58,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you supposed to be advising the practical?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:15.65,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,You're flabbergasted, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:18.00,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,Cake is important for the brain, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:23.33,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Please show him to the bathroom right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:24.08,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:28.45,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,Maria! So it was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.45,0:19:32.41,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,That cake tasted the same as the one\NI had tasted at a school festival in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.41,0:19:33.95,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,It has been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:43.52,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,It was the most delectable sweet I've had in a while. Thank you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.52,0:19:45.21,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You should be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:51.83,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll head back over to Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:54.57,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing special happened thereafter and the day ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:19:59.62,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so tired. I'm so hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:01.47,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's all grab something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:02.84,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:04.14,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have money, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:05.13,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,We'll treat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:05.88,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.88,0:20:07.17,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.17,0:20:08.68,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:11.05,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't she have any pride as a fully grown adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.05,0:20:15.03,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care! I'm going to live as who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:25.22,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,How rare to see her fall asleep at this hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:28.14,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Did she get tired from an environment she's not used to?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:31.14,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Milady was very excited about the plan, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.14,0:20:33.68,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,She was committed to having Maria-san enjoy the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:36.29,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:38.10,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:42.04,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I see, Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:43.99,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,So your fatigue has blown away, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:47.53,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,That's good. I'm always so grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:21:00.75,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,The mansion feels the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:03.16,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about the Thank You Tour?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:06.19,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.19,0:21:07.95,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who should be thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.42,0:21:13.96,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,But, Nagi, Hayate-kun, and the smiles of everyone at the mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:16.95,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the best presents for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:25.92,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:28.37,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue to look after us, Maria-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.37,0:21:28.93,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:32.15,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Maria, your skin looks so smooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.15,0:21:36.38,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Did the Super Special Marvelous\NAnti-Aging Course have an effect?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:37.94,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You're almost like a young girl!
