Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:44.98,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So a seventeen year old isn't a young girl anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.85,0:21:47.80,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Or am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:50.40,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, Maria, you got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.40,0:21:54.45,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,On that note, next week, we'll fight against the sweat perspired from youth.
