Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.13,0:23:37.24,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. It's Asakaze Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.24,0:23:38.66,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the warrior of freedom, Hanabishi Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.66,0:23:42.66,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,All of you in front to the TV,\Nyou've memorized our image song, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.66,0:23:45.14,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm sure they're listening to it at least a hundred times a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.14,0:23:46.81,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,A happy bit of news for people like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.81,0:23:49.59,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,If you collect ten dust covers and send them in...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.59,0:23:50.95,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,...you won't win anything in particular!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.95,0:23:52.07,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.76,0:23:54.92,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,You all must have been waiting. Here's this week's service shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.92,0:23:56.59,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is erotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.59,0:23:58.81,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Starting out so bold so early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.81,0:23:59.85,Default,3,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.30,0:24:04.16,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? Tell me!
