Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.80,0:24:07.57,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Something has to be wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.57,0:24:10.68,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Isumi was wearing a blazer and went off on a bus without getting lost at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.68,0:24:14.60,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she fell in love with a boy in another school\Nand is sneaking into the school wearing their uniform.
